                    <span>Simply put, if you haven't read Competitive Strategy yet, you are unfit to talk about business strategy. <P>And only after reading it, are you fit to read the sequel, Competitive Advantage, which if you haven't read till now, makes you unfit to talk about business tactics.<P>These two books are the Old and New Testaments of business.</span>
                  
              
